data.description:
**Multiple Offers-Final & Best due by Sunday 8Pm**Large corner lot in Timarron Brenwyck neighborhood & walking distance to Rockenbaugh Elementary. Bright, open layout has dining rm formal living & dining rm. HW floors throughout the main floor. Kitchen has island, ss appliances, granite & is open to the living rm with stone fp. Downstairs office has great views of the pool. Full bath downstairs with easy access to pool area. Upstairs is oversized large master bedrm & bathrm with frameless shower, his & her vanities. Guest bedrm with updated private bath, large game rm, Secondary bedrms & updated bathroom. Enjoy the swimming pool, outdoor grill, pergola & plenty of backyard for kids to play.  
All bedrooms up.
